data.description: Remarkable and completely remodeled Cape Cod with over 3,000 square feet of living space, sitting on more than 2 acres and no HOA! A fenced in back yard, established privacy trees, beautiful landscaping, oversized 2 car attached garage with brand new extended driveway and stamped front walkway! There is no shortage of space for those big family gatherings with the huge stamped patio out back and fire pit! Bring the RV and race cars, a separate driveway with ample parking leads to the 30x40 detached garage, oversized garage door, plenty of storage cabinets, and concrete floor! This home has been meticulously maintained and is move-in ready. New windows, roof, HVAC, all new doors, handles and hinges, sliding glass door, new siding, roof, water heater, toilets, vanities, carpet, floors, and countertops, the list goes on.  Enter through the front door off your porch or the other door into the breezeway/mudroom and you will immediately feel like home.  The eat-in kitchen has granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets and an island for additional cooking space. Off the kitchen you will find a large  formal dining room that comfortably fits a table for 10. You also have a separate formal living room that could be used as an office or library, as this home has a huge family room, thick new carpet, complete with a fireplace and doors leading to the back patio.  Down the hall you will find a completely remodeled half bath, a separate laundry room and the hard to come by, main level master suite!  Up stairs there are 3 more large bedrooms and another remodeled full bathroom  and a jacuzzi tub. There is no shortage of storage space in this cape cod with many closets as well as a storage area running the length of the house and another hidden storage area with an access door at the top of the stairs.  Don't miss out on this one, this home has everything complete, ready for you to move in and make it your home. Call and schedule your private showing today!
